    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/dr-patricia-walsh",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 allowances. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all 5 operating points with normalized error below 8%. The ModelConfiguration used for validation (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2) is documented by the solver vendor as differing from the released production build (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7) only in installer manifest handling; no solver algorithmic changes were introduced. The credibility assessment team accepted this equivalence argument without re-running validation under the released build. Credibility assessment is accepted at Medium assurance level for MRL 2.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
  },
